# Preferred UI Styles (Essential)

## Floating Nav (Glass)

- Centered at top; translateX(-50%)
- Background rgba(255,255,255,0.7→0.95 on hover/scroll)
- `backdrop-filter: blur(20px)`, radius 16px, padding 8px 16px
- Shadow: 0 2px 12px → hover 0 6px 24px, border 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3)
- Ref: [src/components/NavBar.tsx](mdc:src/components/NavBar.tsx)

## Contact Chips (Pills)

- inline-flex, gap 8px, padding 8px 12px, radius 9999px
- Base: bg `backgroundLight`, text `textSecondary`, border `borderColor`
- Hover: bg `supportGreen`, text `backgroundWhite`, border `supportGreen`
- Ref: [src/sections/About.tsx](mdc:src/sections/About.tsx)

Use theme tokens from [styled-components.ts](mdc:src/styles/styled-components.ts).
